movieList.description: A secret military project endangers Neo-Tokyo when it turns a biker gang member into a rampaging psychic psychopath.
movieList.title: Akira

movieList.title: Grave of the Fireflies

movieList.description: Two strangers find themselves linked in a bizarre way. When a connection forms, will distance be the only thing to keep them apart?
movieList.title: Your Name

movieList.description: During her family's move to the suburbs, a sullen 10-year-old girl wanders into a world ruled by gods, witches, and spirits, and where humans are changed into beasts.
movieList.title: Spirited Away

movieList.description: On a journey to find the cure for a Tatarigami's curse, Ashitaka finds himself in the middle of a war between the forest gods and Tatara, a mining colony.
movieList.title: Princess Mononoke

movieList.description: When two girls move to the country to be near their ailing mother, they have adventures with the wondrous forest spirits who live nearby.
movieList.title: My Neighbor Totoro

movieList.description: The Bebop crew try to stop a terrorist plan to unleash a deadly virus on Mars.
movieList.title: Cowboy Bebop: The Movie

movieList.description: A cyborg policewoman and her partner hunt a mysterious and powerful hacker called the Puppet Master.
movieList.title: Ghost in the Shell

movieList.description: Warrior and pacifist Princess Nausicaä desperately struggles to prevent two warring nations from destroying themselves and their dying planet.
movieList.title: Nausicaä of the Valley of the Wind

movieList.description: A retired pop singer turned actress' sense of reality is shaken when she is stalked by an obsessed fan and seemingly a ghost of her past.
movieList.title: Perfect Blue

movieList.description: The lives of the Imperial Arm users are truly being tested as they find themselves fighting in a village that has been turned into a Danger Beast feeding ground.
movieList.title: Akame ga Kill! The Movie: The Blackened Village

movieList.description: Eren Yeager and others of the 104th Training Corps have just begun to become full members of the Survey Corps. As they ready themselves to face the Titans once again, their preparations are interrupted by the invasion of Wall Rose.
movieList.title: Attack on Titan: The Roar of Awakening

movieList.description: A poor village under attack by bandits recruits seven unemployed samurai to help them defend themselves.
movieList.title: Seven Samurai

movieList.description: The rape of a bride and the murder of her samurai husband are recalled from the perspectives of four witnesses.
movieList.title: Rashomon

movieList.description: A family of small-time crooks takes in a child they find outside in the cold. They discover clues to the girl's identity while facing various challenges.
movieList.title: Shoplifters

movieList.description: A newly unemployed cellist takes a job preparing the dead for funerals in Japan, where the process provides healing for both the departed and the living.
movieList.title: Departures

movieList.description: In a dystopian future, a class of junior high students is forced to fight to the death under the government's Battle Royale act.
movieList.title: Battle Royale

movieList.description: In Medieval Japan, an aging warlord decides to retire, dividing his kingdom among his three sons, leading to betrayal, war, and tragedy.
movieList.title: Ran

movieList.description: An aging couple travels to Tokyo to visit their grown children but finds they are too busy to spend time with them.
movieList.title: Tokyo Story

movieList.description: A wandering samurai, Sanjuro, plays two rival criminal gangs against each other in a small town.
movieList.title: Yojimbo

movieList.description: When the menace known as The Joker wreaks havoc and chaos on the people of Gotham, Batman must accept one of the greatest psychological and physical tests of his ability to fight injustice.
movieList.title: The Dark Knight

movieList.description: A young lion prince flees his kingdom only to learn the true meaning of responsibility and bravery.
movieList.title: The Lion King

movieList.description: A thief who steals corporate secrets through the use of dream-sharing technology is given the inverse task of planting an idea into the mind of a C.E.O.
movieList.title: Inception

movieList.description: The presidencies of Kennedy and Johnson, the Vietnam War, Watergate, and other historical events unfold from the perspective of an Alabama man with an IQ of 75.
movieList.title: Forrest Gump

movieList.description: Two imprisoned men bond over a number of years, finding solace and eventual redemption through acts of common decency.
movieList.title: The Shawshank Redemption

movieList.description: A computer hacker learns from mysterious rebels about the true nature of his reality and his role in the war against its controllers.
movieList.title: The Matrix

movieList.description: A global cataclysm occurs, threatening the end of the world, as a writer tries to get his family to safety amidst various natural disasters.
movieList.producer: Harald Kloser, Mark Gordon, Larry J. Franco

movieList.description: In Nazi-occupied France during World War II, a plan to assassinate Nazi leaders by a group of Jewish U.S. soldiers coincides with a theater owner's vengeful plans.
movieList.title: Inglourious Basterds

movieList.description: The lives of two mob hitmen, a boxer, a gangster's wife, and a pair of diner bandits intertwine in four tales of violence and redemption.
movieList.title: Pulp Fiction

movieList.description: The aging patriarch of an organized crime dynasty transfers control of his clandestine empire to his reluctant son.
movieList.title: The Godfather

movieList.description: A meek Hobbit from the Shire and eight companions set out on a journey to destroy the powerful One Ring and save Middle-earth from the Dark Lord Sauron.
movieList.title: The Lord of the Rings: The Fellowship of the Ring

movieList.description: Earth's mightiest heroes must come together and learn to fight as a team if they are to stop the mischievous Loki and his alien army from enslaving humanity.
movieList.title: The Avengers

movieList.description: During a preview tour, a theme park suffers a major power breakdown that allows its cloned dinosaur exhibits to run amok.
movieList.title: Jurassic Park

movieList.description: A young FBI cadet must receive the help of an incarcerated and manipulative cannibal killer to help catch another serial killer, a madman who skins his victims.
movieList.title: The Silence of the Lambs

movieList.description: The early life and career of Vito Corleone in 1920s New York City is portrayed while his son, Michael, expands and tightens his grip on the family crime syndicate.
movieList.title: The Godfather: Part II

movieList.description: Eight years after the Joker's reign of anarchy, Batman, with the help of the enigmatic Catwoman, is forced from his exile to save Gotham City from the brutal guerrilla terrorist Bane.
movieList.title: The Dark Knight Rises

movieList.description: An undercover cop and a mole in the police attempt to identify each other while infiltrating an Irish gang in South Boston.
movieList.title: The Departed

movieList.description: A young man is accidentally sent thirty years into the past in a time-traveling DeLorean invented by his friend, Dr. Emmett Brown.
movieList.title: Back to the Future

movieList.description: An insomniac office worker and a devil-may-care soap maker form an underground fight club that evolves into something much more.
movieList.title: Fight Club

movieList.title: Die Hard
